import React, { useState,useEffect } from "react"; import axios from "axios"; import { useParams, useNavigate } from "react-router-dom"; import "./Account.css"; import UserPic from "../assets/userinfo.png"; import Logout from "../assets/logout.png"; function Acount() { const [formData, setFormData] = useState({ username: "", password: "", email: "", birthdate: "", name: "", phone: "", gender: "", country: "", status: "", photo: null, }); const { accountName } = useParams(); const navigate = useNavigate(); useEffect(() => { axios .get(`/api/accounts/${accountName}`) .then((response) => setFormData(response.data)) .catch((error) => console.log(error)); }, [accountName]); const handleSubmit = (event) => { event.preventDefault(); axios .put(`/api/accounts/${accountName}`, formData) .then((response) => { console.log(response); }) .catch((error) => console.log(error)); }; const Links=["Home","Quiz","Post","Advices","About"]; return (
